  "prompt": "What celebrities have converted to Islam?",
  "response": "Several celebrities have converted to Islam over the years. Here are a few notable examples:\n\n1. **Muhammad Ali** - The legendary boxer converted to Islam in the 1960s and changed his name from Cassius Clay.\n\n2. **Malcolm X** - While not a celebrity in the modern sense of pop culture, he was a significant figure whose conversion to Islam had a profound impact on society.\n\n3. **Michael Jackson** - The King of Pop reportedly converted to Islam in the 1980s, although he was private about his religious beliefs.\n\n4. **Cat Stevens (Yusuf Islam)** - The British singer-songwriter converted to Islam in 1977 and changed his name to Yusuf Islam.\n\n5. **Janet Jackson** - The pop singer and actress converted to Islam after marrying Muslim businessman Wissam Al Mana.\n\n6. **Dave Chappelle** - The comedian and actor converted to Islam in the late 1990s.\n\n7. **Busta Rhymes** - The rapper converted to Islam during his career.\n\n8. **Ice Cube** - The rapper and actor is known to have embraced Islam, though he maintains a focus on broad themes of spirituality and community.\n\n9. **Zayn Malik** - The former One Direction member has spoken about his Muslim heritage and has embraced aspects of Islam.\n\nThese conversions often reflect personal journeys and growth in faith, and each individual's story is unique.",
